query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (mc.note like '%Greece%' OR mc.note like '%Germany%') AND it3.info in ('trade mark','LD year','LD quality program','LD aspect ratio','LD digital sound','votes distribution','LD video artifacts','LD number of sides') AND cct1.kind not in ('complete+verified','cast','crew') AND it.info in ('LD sharpness','filming dates','production dates','votes distribution','tech info','LD official retail price','books','LD number of chapter stops','essays','LD contrast') AND t.title not like '%battle%' AND t.title not like '%man%' AND t.title not like '%car%' AND t.title not like '%mirror%' AND t.title not like '%adventure%' AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','crew') AND n.name not like '%a%' AND n.name not like '%x%' AND n.gender not in ('f') AND an.name not like '%d%' AND an.name not like '%p%' AND an.name not like '%f%' AND an.name not like '%c%' AND (chn.name like '%Captain Jack Sparrow%')
